---
// src/components/home/Solution.astro
---
<section class="solution">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="content-wrapper">
      <div class="text-content">
        <h2 class="section-title">Desarrollo Premium a la Medida</h2>
        <p class="section-desc">Diseñamos y construimos plataformas modernas y eficientes que resuelven problemas reales. Dejamos el código espagueti atrás.</p>
        
        <ul class="features">
          <li>
            <strong>Arquitectura Escalable</strong>
            <span>Sistemas preparados para crecer junto a tu negocio sin colapsar.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Experiencia de Usuario (UX)</strong>
            <span>Interfaces limpias e intuitivas que tus clientes amarán usar.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Integraciones Perfectas</strong>
            <span>Conectamos tus sistemas actuales para un flujo de trabajo sin interrupciones.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="visual-content">
        <div class="code-window">
          <div class="window-header">
            <span class="dot red"></span>
            <span class="dot yellow"></span>
            <span class="dot green"></span>
          </div>
          <pre><code><span class="keyword">const</span> success = <span class="function">buildAwesomeSoftware</span>(&#123;
  quality: <span class="string">'premium'</span>,
  stack: <span class="string">'modern'</span>,
  client: <span class="string">'happy'</span>
&#125;);</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .solution {
    padding: 8rem 2rem;
    background-color: #0f172a;
    color: #f8fafc;
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .content-wrapper {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .text-content {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 300px;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: #ffffff;
  }
  .section-desc {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #94a3b8;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .features {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .features li {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }
  .features li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 2px;
    color: #10b981;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }
  .features strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #e2e8f0;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  .features span {
    color: #94a3b8;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .visual-content {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 300px;
  }
  .code-window {
    background: #1e293b;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    transform: perspective(1000px) rotateY(-5deg) rotateX(5deg);
    transition: transform 0.5s ease;
  }
  .code-window:hover {
    transform: perspective(1000px) rotateY(0deg) rotateX(0deg);
  }
  .window-header {
    background: #0f172a;
    padding: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .dot {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .dot.red { background: #ef4444; }
  .dot.yellow { background: #eab308; }
  .dot.green { background: #22c55e; }
  pre {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 2rem;
    font-family: 'Fira Code', monospace;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #e2e8f0;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }
  .keyword { color: #c678dd; }
  .function { color: #61afef; }
  .string { color: #98c379; }
</style>
